OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1784299698
OL,3,CSon found guilty after mother left
OL,4,Cdying on floor for two weeks
OL,6,FA Carlisle man has been found guilty
OL,7,Fof manslaughter, after failing to help
OL,8,Fhis mother who fell and lay on the
OL,9,Fbathroom floor for a fortnight before
OL,10,Fher death.
OL,12,FCarlisle Crown Court heard how Stewart
OL,13,FIrwin, 56, dialled 999 on 28th July,
OL,14,F2023, reporting that Veronica Irwin's
OL,15,Fskin had "started to turn blue" - two
OL,16,Fweeks after she had first fallen over.
OL,18,FIrwin reported that his mother had
OL,19,Fbeen "refusing help" and described her
OL,20,Fas "just one of them stubborn old
OL,21,Fwomen."
OL,26,@wD@JOUwD@_O]{D@FOU{D@TO]|D@DOU
